Kelly LeBrock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kelly_LeBrock 0 Kelly LeBrock (born March 24, 1960) is an American-born English actress and model. Her acting debut was in The Woman in Red (1984), co-starring comic actor Gene Wilder. She also starred in the films Weird Science (1985), directed by John Hughes, and Hard to Kill (1990), with Steven Seagal.
